## Machine teleports between multiverses (discovery)

OPEN QUESTION: What is the first experiment where they suspect they're not just swapping with their own universe? (human)

## Machine teleports between multiverses (divergence)

Between experiments, as they grapple with confusing results or ideas for what to try next, they have life-drama events with themes or inspiration that spark new experiment directions. (human)

The first few multiverse experiments are done on paper, and the team pins results on the wall. Later, when they start sending SD cards with videos of each other, the pinned wall artifacts are still visible in the background and become continuity evidence across universes. (human)

